<i>adverb</i>: 허름히 [허름히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허름히 [허름히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shabbily; raggedly; seedily</dd><br>
<dd>좀 낡은 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being rather old and worn-out.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cheaply; shabbily</dd><br>
<dd>값이 좀 싼 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being rather cheap in price.</dd><br>
<dd>3. shabbily; lowly</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 물건이 표준에 약간 미치지 못한 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of a person or an article being below a certain standard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>